      static class  BasicDiagnosticFormatter.BasicConfiguration.BasicFormatKind
      This enum contains all the kinds of formatting patterns supported by a basic diagnostic formatter.
      static class  BasicDiagnosticFormatter.BasicConfiguration.SourcePosition
      A source positioning value controls the position (within a given diagnostic message) in which the source line the diagnostic refers to should be displayed (if applicable)
